content:
Automate the Running of Data Mask Processes with Job Scheduler

Configure how frequently you run Data Mask, daily, weekly, or monthly, to mask all new data in your sandbox.

This change applies to Lightning Experience and Salesforce Classic in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions where Data Mask is installed.

Available to customers who want to install the latest managed package, 2.1000.
title: Automate Salesforce Data Mask Processes
